Real-time data analytics pipelines and applications on the cloud using Azure HDInsight with Apache Kafka and Apache Spark. 

Streaming real-time to downstream systems, replicating data so there is no single point of failure, and creating a queue of ordered data. Spark is a parallel processing system that takes the data, transform and process
accordignly from the continuous stream of data. Through a batch, or combination of different approaches.

